<br>
It was I who brought up the fact that one of your guildies was cussing. Its not hearsay, it really happened. Unfortunately I do not have a screen shot to back it up. I can however provide alot of details.<br>
<br>
First, it was in north karanas, at the wizard spires. I had just given this halfling warrior from Circle of sisters some shoulders I had looted in Sol B. I gave them to her saying, &quot;A great battle approaches and we may find ourselves fighting side by side. It is important we equip ourselves and be ready!&quot; Etc, etc.<br>
<br>
About a minute later, some folks from your guild appear at the wizard port. This was shortly after some hunting sessions some folks from your guild had in neriak. I was invis, so I made my self visible and started to roleplay with them by demanding the withdrawl of your forces from our cities or face another guildwar.<br>
<br>
Thats when I got the cussing, in /says. (A high elf int caster as I recall but could have been human)<br>
<br>
I thought they were maybe sore about losing the first guildwar, so I let it slide and finished off my &quot;demand&quot; by saying we had acquired a great beast from the lands of Kunark and would set it loose upon your forces should you not comply.<br>
<br>
Thats when I got more cussing, this time in shouts.<br>
<br>
I don't recall swearing myself. I do recall trying to roleplay an ominous, harbinger of doom hehe. But I was quite surprised to get that sort of reaction. In all fairness, I did find out later there was some sort of ugliness about accusations of training etc (either by folks in my guild training you guys or vice versa), flying around. So maybe they were sore about that. Regardless, I still don't think it justified the reaction I got. All of this happened with that female halfling warrior from circle of sisters and a 1st fist of light guy there at the NK wizzie spires. Maybe that will help &quot;jog&quot; some memories about the incident so you can address them.<br>
<br>
I am not bringing this up to slander your guild. Far from it. I want your guild to be as good as you want it to be. I just want you to know that there might be some issues that need to be addressed and I know you are someone who will address things if they are brought to your attention.<br>
<br>
 <p>Kzan Verto<BR>
Giver of "da juice" (tm)
